overview: Welcome to Camp CockyBoys! It's a new series that plays on the nickname for the CockyBoys country home and which takes advantage of the biggest ever gathering of models for our 10th Anniversary Pool Party! Or as one veteran CockyBoy says, "There's a plethora of delectable creatures all walking around at any time". It's a seemingly endless, fun and joyful summer of swimming, canoeing, hiking, etc as well as quiet times getting to know one another. Then there are the nights by the campfire where the models gather for wienie roasting... and true sex confessions!
title: Camp MoreCock
